## Basic Information


### Naming Convention
$APOGEE_REDUX/[APRED]/cal/[INSTRUMENT]/persist/apPersistModel-[CHIP]-[MJD].fits

### Releases

### Enviroments

### Approximate Size
456 MB

### File Type
FITS

### Generated by Product
apogee_drp

False
